definitions.definition: Any plant of the family Cyperaceae .

subdefinitions.definition: Any plant of the genus Carex , the true sedges; perennial herbs with triangular jointless stems, a spiked inflorescence , and long grass-like leaves which are usually rough on the margins and midrib .

definitions.definition: Any of various other plants resembling true sedges, such as Gentiana rubricaulis and Andropogon virginicus .

main_definition: Any plant of the family Cyperaceae .
secondary_definitions: Any of various other plants resembling true sedges, such as Gentiana rubricaulis and Andropogon virginicus .

definitions.definition: ( fishing ) A dry fly used in fly fishing , designed to resemble a sedge or caddis fly .

main_definition: ( fishing ) A dry fly used in fly fishing , designed to resemble a sedge or caddis fly .

definitions.definition: A flock of herons , cranes , or bitterns .

secondary_definitions: A flock of herons , cranes , or bitterns .
